	(279,'soco_directions','[column-wrap][column size=\\\\\\\'one-fourth\\\\\\\'][column-heading]From North Orlando[/column-heading]<p>Interstate 4 west to downtown Orlando, exit at Colonial Drive/Centroplex, turn left on Colonial Drive, heading east. Turn right on Orange Avenue, heading south towards downtown. Turn left on Central Boulevard, heading east. Soco is located a few blocks east at 629 East Central Boulevard.</p>[/column][column size=\\\\\\\'one-fourth\\\\\\\'][column-heading]From South Orlando[/column-heading]<p>Interstate 4 east to downtown Orlando, exit at Amelia Street/Centroplex, turn right on Amelia Street, heading east. Turn right on Orange Avenue, heading south towards downtown. Turn left on Central Boulevard, heading east. Soco is located a few blocks east at 629 East Central Boulevard.</p>[/column][column size=\\\\\\\'one-fourth\\\\\\\'][column-heading]From East Orlando[/column-heading]<p>State Road 408 (East âWest Expressway) west to downtown Orlando. Exit at Mills Avenue and travel west on South Street towards downtown Orlando. Turn right heading north on Summerlin Avenue. Turn left on Central Boulevard, heading west. Soco is located on your right at 629 East Central Boulevard.</p>[/column][column size=\\\\\\\'one-fourth\\\\\\\'][column-heading]From West Orlando[/column-heading]<p>State Road 408 (East âWest Expressway) east to downtown Orlando, exit at Orange Avenue (State Road 527) and follow signs north on Orange Avenue to downtown Orlando. Orange Avenue becomes Rosalind Avenue. Turn right on Central Boulevard, heading east. Soco is located a few blocks east at 629 East Central Boulevard.</p>[/column][/column-wrap]','yes'),
